10typedef void (*poly1305_blocks_f) (void *ctx, const unsigned char *inp,
11 size_t len, unsigned int padbit);
12typedef void (*poly1305_emit_f) (void *ctx, unsigned char mac[16],
13 const unsigned int nonce[4]);
14
15struct poly1305_context {
16 double opaque[24]; /* large enough to hold internal state, declared
17 * 'double' to ensure at least 64-bit invariant
18 * alignment across all platforms and
19 * configurations */
20 unsigned int nonce[4];
21 unsigned char data[POLY1305_BLOCK_SIZE];
22 size_t num;
23 struct {
24 poly1305_blocks_f blocks;
25 poly1305_emit_f emit;
26 } func;
27};
